<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Art Styles Guide</title>

<style>
body {
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
  margin: 0;
  background: #f5f5f7;
  color: #1d1d1f;
}

.container {
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: auto;
  padding: 20px;
}

h1 {
  font-size: 28px;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.section {
  background: white;
  border-radius: 16px;
  padding: 20px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.slider {
  display: flex;
  overflow-x: auto;
  gap: 10px;
  margin: 15px 0;
}

.slider img {
  width: 250px;
  height: 250px;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 12px;
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.prompt {
  background: #f2f2f2;
  padding: 10px;
  border-radius: 10px;
  font-size: 14px;
  direction: ltr;
}
</style>

</head>

<body>
<div class="container">

<h1>Art Styles Guide</h1>

<!-- SURREALISM -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Surrealism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?surreal,art">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?dreamlike,art">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?fantasy,concept">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Surrealism, dreamlike scene, unexpected objects, symbolic imagery, irrational composition
</div>
</div>

<!-- CUBISM -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Cubism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?cubism,art">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?geometric,portrait">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Cubism, fragmented geometry, multiple viewpoints, structured composition
</div>
</div>

<!-- IMPRESSIONISM -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Impressionism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?impressionism,painting">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?soft,brush,painting">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Impressionism, loose brush strokes, light-driven colors, soft edges
</div>
</div>

<!-- MINIMALISM -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Minimalism</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?minimal,design">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?clean,white,design">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Minimalism, very few elements, strong negative space, clean composition
</div>
</div>

<!-- CYBERPUNK -->
<div class="section">
<h2>Cyberpunk</h2>

<div class="slider">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?cyberpunk,city">
<img src="https://source.unsplash.com/300x300/?neon,futuristic">
</div>

<div class="prompt">
Cyberpunk, neon lighting, futuristic city, dark atmosphere, high contrast
</div>
</div>

</div>
</body>
</html>
